WEBVTT

00:01:38.500 --> 00:01:44.300
"Unfold"

00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:47.500
(Episode 3)

00:02:13.916 --> 00:02:14.916
Sorry.

00:02:15.166 --> 00:02:16.166
I'm late.

00:03:16.291 --> 00:03:17.291
Your hand.

00:03:23.083 --> 00:03:24.416
Why don't you wear gloves?

00:03:25.208 --> 00:03:26.208
Isn't it cold?

00:03:37.958 --> 00:03:39.500
Lao Bai died inexplicably.

00:03:40.083 --> 00:03:42.708
Now, people all over the
world think I fucking killed him.

00:03:43.458 --> 00:03:44.458
Go and investigate.

00:03:48.541 --> 00:03:49.541
What's wrong?

00:03:50.375 --> 00:03:50.958
Nothing.

00:03:51.375 --> 00:03:52.375
Understood.

00:03:55.250 --> 00:03:56.250
Go ahead.

00:04:42.500 --> 00:04:46.083
Why does Young Master Zhao have
the time to come and see this old man?

00:04:55.416 --> 00:04:56.875
I have to come even if I'm busy.

00:05:01.916 --> 00:05:02.583
Uncle Bai,

00:05:02.833 --> 00:05:03.833
Sit down.

00:05:04.500 --> 00:05:05.500
This is your home.

00:05:11.791 --> 00:05:13.166
I heard from my dad,

00:05:13.791 --> 00:05:15.375
this house was built by him for you.

00:05:17.625 --> 00:05:18.458
It is.

00:05:18.583 --> 00:05:20.208
Elder brother is kind-hearted.

00:05:21.291 --> 00:05:22.333
Is he kind-hearted?

00:05:25.000 --> 00:05:26.250
He is.

00:05:27.875 --> 00:05:28.875
Uncle Bai,

00:05:29.375 --> 00:05:31.041
My dad is quite careless,

00:05:31.125 --> 00:05:32.445
he doesn't like keeping accounts.

00:05:34.416 --> 00:05:35.708
But I heard,

00:05:37.291 --> 00:05:38.541
Uncle Bai has this habit.

00:05:42.583 --> 00:05:43.583
Young Master Zhao,

00:05:43.833 --> 00:05:45.273
you're going to audit the accounts?

00:05:53.791 --> 00:05:55.083
Forget about the past,

00:05:57.034 --> 00:05:59.201
but I want to know from the ten years,

00:06:01.208 --> 00:06:02.928
where has all the money from the port gone?

00:06:05.250 --> 00:06:07.375
As for the dirty deeds you have committed,

00:06:07.666 --> 00:06:08.958
I'm not interested in knowing.

00:06:10.541 --> 00:06:11.708
The port's accounts,

00:06:11.916 --> 00:06:13.684
have always been managed personally
by the eldest brother.

00:06:13.708 --> 00:06:14.708
On my side,

00:06:15.409 --> 00:06:16.729
I just keep track of ends and odds.

00:06:20.730 --> 00:06:21.930
Even ends and odds are fine.

00:06:30.875 --> 00:06:32.375
Young Master Zhao,

00:06:32.458 --> 00:06:34.208
you don't trust me anymore.

00:06:36.083 --> 00:06:37.375
Uncle Bai is joking.

00:06:39.083 --> 00:06:40.540
Recently, there was a buyer

00:06:40.564 --> 00:06:42.064
that has set his sights on that port.

00:06:42.833 --> 00:06:44.875
I want to see how the recent earnings are.

00:06:45.083 --> 00:06:46.333
You want to sell the port?

00:06:47.500 --> 00:06:48.500
No.

00:06:49.166 --> 00:06:50.291
Even if I agree,

00:06:50.583 --> 00:06:52.416
other shareholders will not agree either.

00:07:00.916 --> 00:07:02.375
If I remember correctly,

00:07:02.791 --> 00:07:04.208
that port,

00:07:11.791 --> 00:07:13.151
let's stick with the surname Zhao.

00:07:20.416 --> 00:07:21.541
I didn't mean that.

00:07:22.458 --> 00:07:23.666
I mean,

00:07:23.833 --> 00:07:26.040
My older brother
particularly likes this port,

00:07:26.041 --> 00:07:26.833
and,

00:07:27.000 --> 00:07:28.000
it has stable earnings.

00:07:28.250 --> 00:07:29.666
There is no need to sell now.

00:07:33.791 --> 00:07:34.791
Is that so?

00:07:36.708 --> 00:07:37.957
Didn't you just say,

00:07:37.958 --> 00:07:39.478
all the account books are with my dad?

00:07:40.416 --> 00:07:41.875
How can you be so sure

00:07:42.166 --> 00:07:43.566
that the income has stabilized now?

00:07:59.250 --> 00:08:00.250
I'm going, Uncle Bai.

00:08:02.541 --> 00:08:03.541
I'll see myself out.

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:09.280
I'll wait for your account book.

00:08:58.708 --> 00:09:02.953
How have all these organ donor appeared half
a month after the patient was hospitalized?

00:13:18.166 --> 00:13:19.166
You will get cold.

00:13:23.541 --> 00:13:25.661
The temperature is
set to 28 degrees Celsius.

00:13:29.125 --> 00:13:30.226
There is still some in the pot,

00:13:30.250 --> 00:13:31.250
pour it yourself.

00:13:39.583 --> 00:13:40.791
Lao Wu said

00:13:42.875 --> 00:13:44.083
I killed Lao Bai,

00:13:47.666 --> 00:13:49.466
his equity wouldn't be sold to me,

00:13:50.291 --> 00:13:51.333
so I killed him.

00:14:20.083 --> 00:14:21.083
Good-looking.

00:14:21.625 --> 00:14:22.625
What?

00:14:30.916 --> 00:14:32.596
Why don't you ask me why I took the photo?

00:14:34.208 --> 00:14:35.208
Why?

00:14:40.583 --> 00:14:41.291
Hello.

00:14:41.583 --> 00:14:43.333
Are you a friend of A'Che?

00:14:43.541 --> 00:14:45.741
It's the first time I see
a friend coming to visit him.

00:14:46.166 --> 00:14:46.708
Hello.

00:14:46.791 --> 00:14:47.791
My name is Zhou Chen.

00:14:47.958 --> 00:14:48.958
Sister Xiao Yun.

00:14:49.083 --> 00:14:51.892
He had worked with my father before,
he came to talk to me about something.

00:14:51.916 --> 00:14:53.125
We're gonna go out for a bit.

00:14:54.125 --> 00:14:55.875
Are you a supplier of used books?

00:14:56.500 --> 00:14:58.100
Why haven't I heard the boss mention it?

00:15:02.833 --> 00:15:03.708
No.

00:15:03.833 --> 00:15:05.000
It's something else.

00:15:05.875 --> 00:15:06.875
I see.

00:15:07.041 --> 00:15:08.666
We'll take our leave now.